{"tid":1184231,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"成班傻閪仲話醬油蟹冇蟲冇菌","createTime":"2019-06-03T13:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T02:39:55.000Z","uid":225567,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8ecb97616e14d64b1b128312779f9b912dbde8d1","tid":1184231,"uid":225567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"浙江婦食醬油蟹，造成多重器官功能障礙。網上圖片浙江一名中年婦近日吃了半隻醬油蟹後，出現上吐下瀉、冒冷汗等情況，家人發現立刻將她送醫。<br />\n<br />\n醫生指女子最高體溫達到40.5℃，是典型感染表現，病人除了出現無尿、神智不清等情況，進一步檢查後更發現，她的肝腎、心肌功能也進一步惡化，已經造成多重器官功能障礙，目前只能透過藥物、插管維生。<br />\n<br />\n李惠利東部醫院重症監護室主任董縐縐表示，醃製海鮮變質後，含有大量的副溶血性弧菌和其他細菌，進食或造成食物中毒。他提醒有些病人因肝功能不好，免疫力降低可能出現休克、昏迷等情況，嚴重者還可能奪命，提醒吃下肚前切記要洗乾淨並煮熟再食用，煮熟後也得注意別存放過久。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvcQQHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvcQQHQ.jpg&h=418575f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource ：<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1514164/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1514164%2F&d=TytWRGNO3s0Eety5H3eokxjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=806fbf6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1514164%2F&h=9b1fa443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1514164/</a>"},{"pid":"9574e0632600c5d9f2ef98b3d5931bbee34ed364","tid":1184231,"uid":225567,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T13:31:07.000Z","msg":"班港女仲特登去韓國食蟲蟹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048c9a3500c8293bffd3dcf2b590912b6f886a75","tid":1184231,"uid":186882,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T14:34:37.000Z","msg":"韓國好多野食都on9 到無人有"},{"pid":"7f680200757a3d7b0eb97c3078200326